completions.md
     1Ôćĺ# The completions command
     3ÔćĺThe completions command is used to generate auto-completions for some common shells.
     4ÔćĺThis means when you type `mdbook` in your shell, you can then press your shell's auto-complete key (usually the Tab key) and it may display what the valid options are, or finish partial input.
